videos.description: On their first play of the game, Tua Tagovailoa completes a pass to Henry Ruggs III who burns the Aggies' defense for a 75-yard Alabama touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ruggs breaks out for 75-yard Alabama TD) 2019/09/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ruggs breaks out for 75-yard Alabama TD

videos.description: Tua Tagovailoa connects with a streaking Jerry Jeudy who scores a 21-yard Alabama touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tua finds Jeudy for 2nd TD pass of the day) 2019/09/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tua finds Jeudy for 2nd TD pass of the day

videos.description: Tua Tagovailoa connects with Jerry Jeudy for a second time to score a 23-yard touchdown at the end of the 1st quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tua connects with Jeudy for 23-yard TD) 2019/09/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tua connects with Jeudy for 23-yard TD

videos.description: Tua Tagovailoa breaks out of the pocket and runs 25 yards for a touchdown to give Alabama a 35-0 lead over New Mexico State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tua takes off for 25-yard TD) 2019/09/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tua takes off for 25-yard TD

videos.description: Tua Tagovailoa throws for 227 yards and three touchdowns as the Crimson Tide take down the Aggies 62-10 in dominating fashion.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Alabama dominates New Mexico State 62-10) 2019/09/07 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Alabama dominates New Mexico State 62-10
